<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="290" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,331,1582]" pageId="1" pageNumber="290">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1519,1545]" pageId="1" pageNumber="290">Etymology.</emphasis>
This species is named in honour of the Czech lepidopterist Ing. Josef Procházka (Nižbor, 
<collectingCountry name="Czech Republic" pageId="1" pageNumber="290">Czech Republic</collectingCountry>
) who was interested in 
